author: Demonness
text:
Disclaimer that most everything I know, I learned from others and even deities.

Like attracts like, so when you want something, get into the mindset that you already have it. If you send out wanting energy, it creates blockages, making it harder to receive those things.

author: Demonness
text: Did you know that if you get a journal book or a diary (anything you can write in), and pour your loving energy into it (kiss it, dote on it, talk to it, etc); write what you want to have as if you already have it, you will either recieve or be able to purchase those things?
